<br>
I've stated in the past that this is terrible, since any secondary mages will not be able to get that damage, and so their DPS will suck.<br>
<br>
If these spells go live and druids are able to get these spells, then your ubermage DPS will decrease by about 20-30% as you will not be the one casting damage shields.<br>
<br>
An insiginificant increase in pet damage output and nuke DPS is hardly going to make up for that.<br>
