My opinions on the Druid spells?<br>
<br>
DS - Our DS has always lasted longer than yours, but been a point less.  No real distinction, probably worked out even in the end.  But no, I didn't want this.  I already have a 32 point DS, what's two friggin points?!<br>
<br>
Nukes - Our nukes are better than yours for the most part, but we tend to get resisted more.  Plus you have a pet(yes, I know, pathing quite frankly sucks and you have my sympathy), but under ideal situations where we use every tool at hand, you guys out damage us.  Don't bitch at druids because of our nukes.  Verant needs to put some serious work into your pets.  I got a 100 point improve.  Want to bet it gets resisted just as much? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Bulwark - Cleric spell  ac30, 350hp, 7 mana regen?!  See any resemblance to PoTG?  ac24 450HP 6 mana regen.  cleric spell has higher AC so will overwrite druid spell.  It's single spell, so cleric buff tanks with aegolism and casters with bulwark.  No need for druids now.  Period.<br>
<br>
Don't complain about us druids.  I recognize the needs for your class.  These spells do nothing for us.  When the other classes are raiding the mages and druids can sit in the corner and argue about who can do the most damage solo....behind necros of course.<br>
